    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='221:248'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '029-1a' );" name="029-1a" class="pb">[029-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='248:264'>禮記要義卷第三十　投壷　儒行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='264:275'>一奉矢奉中執壷之節</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='275:295'>投壷之禮主人奉矢司射奉中使人執壷注云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='295:315'>矢所以投者也中士則鹿中也射人奉之者投</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='315:335'>壷射之類也其奉之西階上北靣正義曰士則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='335:355'>鹿中案射記云大夫兕中士鹿中此篇投壷是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='355:375'>大夫士之禮故云士則鹿中不云兕中者略之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='375:395'>也知此投壷是大夫士禮者以經云主人請賔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='395:415'>是平敵之辭與郷飲酒郷射同故知是大夫士</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='415:442'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '029-1b' );" name="029-1b" class="pb">[029-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='442:462'>也若諸侯則燕禮大射毎事云請於公不得云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='462:482'>主人請賔也此旣非諸侯之禮而經云奏貍首</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='482:502'>者別取燕飲之義非謂尊卑之詩其諸侯相燕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='502:522'>亦有投壷故左傳云晉侯與齊侯燕投壷然則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='522:542'>天子亦有之但古禮亡無以知也其中之形刻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='542:562'>木爲之狀如兕鹿而伏背上立圎圈以盛筭云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='562:582'>奉之西階上北靣者案鄉射禮將射之時司射</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='582:602'>升自西階階上北靣告於賔故知此司射奉中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='602:622'>在西階上北靣其執壷之人賤於司射故在司</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='622:649'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '029-2a' );" name="029-2a" class="pb">[029-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='649:669'>射之西以凡行禮統於主人雖俱在西階而當</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='669:689'>尊東故燕禮大射宰夫代公爲主人與賔俱升</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='689:699'>西階而主人在東也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='699:710'>五受矢揖賔即席之節</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='710:730'>巳拜受矢進即兩楹間退反位揖賔就筵注云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='730:750'>主人旣拜送矢又自受矢進即兩楹間者言將</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='750:770'>有事於此也退乃揖賔即席欲與偕進明爲偶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='770:790'>也賔席主人席皆南郷間相去如射物正義曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='790:810'>云退乃揖賔者解經退反位揖賔也所以揖之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='810:837'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '029-2b' );" name="029-2b" class="pb">[029-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='837:857'>者欲與賔俱即席相對爲偶而共投壷云賔席</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='857:877'>主人席皆南郷間相去如射物者以壷在於南</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='877:897'>故知投壷南郷也投壷是射之類故知席相去</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='897:917'>如射物也物謂射者所立之處物長三尺闊一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='917:937'>尺二寸兩物東西相去容一弓故郷射記云物</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='937:957'>長如笴其間容弓距隨長武注云笴長三尺距</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='957:965'>隨者物横畫也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='965:974'>六司射度壷設中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='974:994'>司射進度壷間以二矢半反位設中東面執八</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='994:1021'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '029-3a' );" name="029-3a" class="pb">[029-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1021:1041'>筭興注云度壷度其所設之處也壷去坐二矢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1041:1061'>半則堂上去賔席主人席邪行各七尺也反位</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1061:1081'>西階上位也設中東靣旣設中亦實八筭於中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1081:1101'>横委其餘於中西執筭而立以請賔俟投正義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1101:1121'>曰間以二矢半者投壷有三處室中堂上及庭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1121:1141'>中也日中則於室日晚則於堂大晚則於庭是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1141:1161'>各隨光明故也矢有長短亦隨地廣狹室中狹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1161:1181'>矢長五扶堂上稍廣矢長七扶庭中大廣矢長</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1181:1201'>九扶四指曰扶扶廣四寸五扶者則二尺也七</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1201:1228'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '029-3b' );" name="029-3b" class="pb">[029-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1228:1248'>扶者則二尺八寸也九扶者則三尺六寸也雖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1248:1268'>矢有長短而度壷皆使去賔主之席各二矢半</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1268:1288'>也室中去席五尺堂上則去席七尺庭中則去</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1288:1293'>席九尺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1293:1311'>　八司射告賔主以投壷之法行爵立馬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1311:1331'>請賔曰順投爲入比投不釋勝飲不勝者正爵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1331:1351'>旣行請爲勝者立馬一馬從二馬三馬旣立請</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1351:1371'>慶多馬請主人亦如之注云請猶告也順投矢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1371:1391'>夲入也比投不拾也勝飲不勝言以能養不能</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1391:1418'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '029-4a' );" name="029-4a" class="pb">[029-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1418:1438'>也正爵所以正禮之爵也或以罰或以慶馬勝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1438:1458'>筭也謂之馬者若云投藝如此任爲將帥乗馬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1458:1478'>也射投壷皆所以習武因爲樂正義曰此一經</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1478:1498'>明司射告賔主以投壷之法　順投爲入者司</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1498:1518'>射執八筭起而告賔黨爲投壷之法也順夲也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1518:1538'>言矢有本末投矢於壷以矢夲入者乃名爲入</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1538:1558'>則爲之釋筭也若矢以末入則不名爲入亦不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1558:1577'>爲之釋筭也比投不釋者比頻也又賔主投</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1577:1597'>壷法要更遞而投不得以前旣入喜恱不待後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1597:1624'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '029-4b' );" name="029-4b" class="pb">[029-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1624:1644'>人投之而已頻頻投雖入亦不爲之釋筭也一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1644:1664'>馬從二馬者毎一勝輙立一馬禮以三馬爲成</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1664:1684'>若專三馬則爲一成但勝偶未必專頻得三若</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1684:1704'>勝偶得二劣偶得一旣劣於二故徹取劣偶之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1704:1724'>一以足勝偶之二爲三故云一馬從二馬然定</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1724:1744'>夲無此一句　三馬旣立請慶多馬者若頻得</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1744:1764'>三成或取彼足爲三馬是其勝已成又酌酒慶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1764:1773'>賀於多馬之偶也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1773:1787'>　九弦者奏貍首與郷射小異</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1787:1814'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '029-5a' );" name="029-5a" class="pb">[029-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1814:1834'>命弦者曰請奏貍首間若一大師曰諾注云弦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1834:1854'>鼓瑟者也貍首詩篇名也今逸射義所云詩曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1854:1874'>曽孫侯氏是也間若一者投壷當以爲志取節</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1874:1895'>焉正義曰案郷射三畨𥘉一畨耦射不釋筭第</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1895:1916'>二畨釋筭未作樂第三畨乃用樂此投壷發𥘉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='1916:1933'>則用樂者以投壷禮輕主於歡樂故也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='1933:1945'>　十司射釋獲如數射筭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='1945:1965'>卒投司射執筭曰左右卒投請數二筭爲純一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='1965:1985'>純以取一筭爲竒遂以竒筭告曰某賢於某若</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='1985:2012'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '029-5b' );" name="029-5b" class="pb">[029-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='2012:2032'>干純竒則曰竒鈞則曰左右鈞注云卒巳也賔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2032:2052'>主之黨畢巳投司射又請數其所釋左右筭如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2052:2072'>數射筭一純以取實於左手十純則縮而委之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2072:2092'>毎委異之有餘則横諸純下一筭爲竒竒則縮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2092:2112'>諸純下兼斂左筭實於左手一純以委十則異</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2112:2132'>之其他如右獲畢則司射執竒筭以告於賔與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2132:2152'>主人也若告云某賢於某者未斥主黨勝與賔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2152:2172'>黨勝與以勝爲賢尚枝藝也鈞猶等也等則左</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2172:2192'>右手各執一筭以告正義曰云如數射筭者以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2192:2219'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '029-6a' );" name="029-6a" class="pb">[029-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2219:2239'>投壷之類故知此數投壷之筭如數射筭云一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2239:2259'>純以取至其他如右獲此皆郷射之禮文也一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2259:2279'>純以取實於左手謂就地上之筭以右手毎一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2279:2299'>純別而取實於左手云十純則縮而委之每委</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2299:2319'>異之者滿十純則從而委之於地司射東靣則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2319:2339'>東西爲縮每十雙則東西縮爲一委毎有十雙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2339:2359'>更别委之故云每委異之云有餘則横諸純下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2359:2379'>者有餘謂不滿十雙或八雙九雙以下則横於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2379:2399'>純下謂横在十純之西南北置之云一筭爲竒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2399:2426'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '029-6b' );" name="029-6b" class="pb">[029-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2426:2446'>竒則縮諸純下者若唯有一筭則縮之零純之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2446:2466'>下在零純之西東西置之此謂數右筭之法若</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2466:2486'>數左筭則異於右筭謂揔歛地之筭實於左手</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2486:2506'>之中毎一純取以委地滿十則異之謂滿十純</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2506:2526'>揔爲一委云其他如右獲者謂所縱所横如右</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2526:2530'>獲也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2530:2543'><span class='krp-note'>十/一</span>酌者飲者之節</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2543:2563'>命酌曰請行觴酌者曰諾當飲者皆跪而奉觴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2563:2583'>曰賜灌勝者跪曰敬養注曰司射又請於賔與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2583:2610'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '029-7a' );" name="029-7a" class="pb">[029-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2610:2630'>主人以行正爵酌者勝黨之弟子酌者亦酌奠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2630:2650'>於豐上不勝者坐取乃退而跪飲之灌猶飲也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2650:2670'>言賜灌者服而爲尊敬辭也周禮曰以灌賔客</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2670:2688'>賜灌敬養各與其偶於西階上如飲射爵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2688:2707'><span class='krp-note'>十/二</span>投壷立三馬與郷射立耦小異</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2707:2727'>正爵旣行請立馬馬各直其筭一馬從二馬以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2727:2747'>慶慶禮曰三馬旣備請慶多馬賔主皆曰諾注</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2747:2767'>云飲不勝者畢司射又請爲勝者立馬當其所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='2767:2787'>釋筭之前三立馬者投壷如射亦三而止也三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='2787:2814'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '029-7b' );" name="029-7b" class="pb">[029-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='2814:2834'>者一黨不必三勝其一勝者并其馬於再勝者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='2834:2854'>以慶之明一勝不得慶也飲慶爵者偶親酌不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='2854:2874'>使弟子無豐正義曰一馬從二馬者投壷與射</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='2874:2894'>禮同亦三畨而止每畨勝者則立一馬假令賔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='2894:2914'>黨三畨俱勝則立三馬或賔黨兩勝而立二馬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='2914:2934'>主黨一勝但立一馬即以主黨從就賔黨二馬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='2934:2955'>以少足益於多以助勝者爲榮案郷射禮𥘉畨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='2955:2975'>三耦射但唱獲而巳未釋筭亦未飲不勝者第</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='2975:2995'>二畨耦射畢賔主之黨皆射畢乃數筭飲不勝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='2995:3022'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '029-8a' );" name="029-8a" class="pb">[029-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='3022:3042'>者第三畨三耦及賔主等皆射中鼓節乃爵筭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='3042:3064'>飲罰爵今投壷𥘉則不立三耦唯賔主三畨而止</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='3064:3080'><span class='krp-note'>十/三</span>矢長短壷廣狹席逺近</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='3080:3100'>籌室中五扶堂上七扶庭中九扶筭長尺二寸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='3100:3120'>壷頸脩七寸腹脩五寸口徑二寸半容斗五升</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='3120:3140'>壷中實小豆焉爲其矢之躍而岀也壷去席二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='3140:3160'>矢半矢以柘若棘毋去其皮注曰籌矢也鋪四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='3160:3180'>指曰扶一指案寸春秋傳曰膚寸而合投壷者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3180:3200'>或於室或於堂或於庭其禮䙝隨晏早之宜無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='3200:3227'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '029-8b' );" name="029-8b" class="pb">[029-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3227:3247'>常處其節三扶可也或曰筭長尺有握握素也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3247:3267'>脩長也腹容斗五升三分益一則爲二斗得圜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3267:3287'>囷之象積三百二十四寸也以腹脩五寸約之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3287:3307'>所得求其圜周圜周二尺七寸有竒是爲腹徑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3307:3327'>九寸有餘也實以小豆取其滑且堅以柘棘取</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3327:3347'>其堅且重也舊說云矢大七分或言去其皮節</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3347:3367'>正義曰今檢鄭之文注之意以二斗整數計之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3367:3387'>不取經文斗五升之義故云圜周二尺七寸有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3387:3407'>竒今筭者以其二尺七寸之圍必受斗五升之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3407:3434'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '029-9a' );" name="029-9a" class="pb">[029-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3434:3454'>物數不相㑹也云壷體腹之上下各漸減殺苟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3454:3463'>欲望合恐非鄭意</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3463:3476'><span class='krp-note'>十/四</span>魯薛令弟子辭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3476:3496'>魯令弟子辭曰毋幠毋敖毋偝立毋踰言偝立</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3496:3516'>踰言有常爵薛令弟子辭曰毋幠毋敖毋偝立</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='3516:3536'>毋踰言若是者浮注云弟子賔黨主黨年穉者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='3536:3556'>也爲其立堂下相䙝慢司射戒令之記魯薛者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='3556:3576'>禮衰乖異不知孰是也幠敖慢也偝立不正郷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='3576:3596'>前也踰言逺談語也常爵常所以罰人之爵也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='3596:3623'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '029-9b' );" name="029-9b" class="pb">[029-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3623:3643'>浮亦謂是也晏子春秋曰酌者奉觴而進曰君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3643:3663'>令浮晏子時以罰梁丘據浮或作匏或作符踰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3663:3668'>或爲淫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='3668:3683'><span class='krp-note'>十/五</span>魯薛投壷射禮皷節</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='3683:3703'>取半以下爲投壷禮盡用之爲射禮注云此魯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='3703:3723'>薛擊鼓之節也圜者擊鼙方者擊鼔古者舉事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='3723:3743'>鼓各有節聞其節則知其事矣投壷之鼔半射</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='3743:3757'>節者投壷射之細也射謂燕射</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='3757:3770'><span class='krp-note'>十/六</span>投壷有賔主黨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='3770:3798'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '029-10a' );" name="029-10a" class="pb">[029-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='3798:3818'>司射庭長及冠士立者皆屬賔黨樂人及使者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='3818:3838'>童子皆屬主黨注云庭長司正也使者主人所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='3838:3858'>使薦羞者樂人國子能爲樂者此皆與於投壷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='3858:3878'>正義曰庭長司正也冠士者謂外人來觀投壷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='3878:3898'>成人加冠之士尊之故令屬賔黨若童子賤則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='3898:3918'>屬主黨也云樂人國子能爲樂者以國子習樂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='3918:3938'>故云國子能爲樂者欲明此樂人非瞽矇視瞭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='3938:3958'>之徒以其能與主人之黨而觀禮故知非作樂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='3958:3978'>瞽人也案國子是王子公卿大夫元士之子今</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='3978:4006'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '029-10b' );" name="029-10b" class="pb">[029-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='4006:4026'>來觀樂士大夫投壷者以國之俊選皆在學習</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='4026:4036'>樂共士子來觀投壷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='4036:4053'><span class='krp-note'>十/七</span>衣少所居服冠長所居冠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='4053:4073'>丘少居魯衣逢掖之衣長居宋冠章甫之冠丘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='4073:4093'>聞之也君子之學也博其服也郷丘不知儒服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='4093:4114'>注云逢猶大也大掖之衣大𬒮禪衣也此君子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='4114:4134'>有道藝者所衣也孔子生魯長而之宋而冠焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='4134:4154'>宋其祖所出也衣少所居之服冠長所居之冠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='4154:4174'>是之謂郷言不知儒服非哀公意不在於儒乃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='4174:4202'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '029-11a' );" name="029-11a" class="pb">[029-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='4202:4222'>今問其服庶人禪衣袂二尺二寸祛尺二寸正</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='4222:4243'>義曰庶人禪衣𬒮二尺二寸者庶人無朝祭之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='4243:4264'>事故知禪衣𬒮二尺二寸云祛尺二寸者玉藻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='4264:4284'>文言深衣之制如此今夫子著禪衣與庶人同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='4284:4306'>其𬒮大與庶人異故謂衣爲逢掖也則此大𬒮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='4306:4326'>深衣也長居宋冠章甫之冠言夫子生於魯長</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='4326:4348'>於宋魯有大𬒮禪衣宋有章甫之冠故知大𬒮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='4348:4368'>之衣是少所居之服也章甫之冠是長所居之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='4368:4388'>冠案曲禮云去國三丗唯興之日從新國之法</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='4388:4416'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '029-11b' );" name="029-11b" class="pb">[029-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='4416:4436'>孔子曽祖防叔防叔生木金木金生伯夏伯夏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='4436:4456'>生良紇良紇生孔子防叔奔魯至孔子五丗應</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='4456:4476'>從魯冠而猶著殷章甫冠者以丘爲制法之主</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='4476:4496'>故有異於人所行之事多用殷禮不與㝷常同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='4496:4516'>也且曲禮從新國之法秪謂禮儀法用未必衣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='4516:4536'>服盡從也禮臣朝於君應著朝服而著常服者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='4536:4556'>時孔子自衞新還哀公館之非是常朝故衣冠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='4556:4560'>異也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='4560:4575'><span class='krp-note'>十/八</span>麤而翹之又不急爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='4575:4603'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '029-12a' );" name="029-12a" class="pb">[029-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='4603:4623'>陳言而伏静而正之上弗知也麤而翹之又不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='4623:4643'>急爲也注云麤猶䟽也微也君不知己有善言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='4643:4663'>正行則觀色縁事而微翹發其意使知之又必</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='4663:4683'>舒而脫脫焉巳爲之疾則君納之速君納之速</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='4683:4691'>怪妬所由生也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='4691:4708'><span class='krp-note'>十/九</span>孔子作儒行自衞反魯時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='4708:4728'>今衆人之命儒也妄常以儒相詬病孔子至舎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='4728:4748'>哀公館之聞此言也言加信行加義終没吾丗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='4748:4768'>不敢以儒爲戲注云妄之言無也言今丗名儒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='4768:4796'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '029-12b' );" name="029-12b" class="pb">[029-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='4796:4816'>無有常人遭人名爲儒而以儒靳故相戲此哀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='4816:4836'>公輕儒之所由也詬病猶恥辱也儒行之作蓋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='4836:4857'>孔子自衞𥘉反魯時也孔子歸至其舎哀公就</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='4857:4877'>而以禮館之問儒服而遂問儒行乃始覺焉言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='4877:4890'>没丗不敢以儒爲戲當時服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='4890:4903'><span class='krp-note'>二/十</span>歷叙孔子不遇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='4903:4923'>案史記孔子丗家云在魯哀公不用在齊犂鉏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='4923:4943'>所毁入楚子西所譛適晉趙鞅欲害伐樹於宋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='4943:4964'>削跡於衞畏匡厄陳則身𬒳辱累多矣鄭以其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='4964:4992'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '029-13a' );" name="029-13a" class="pb">[029-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='4992:5012'>如此故釋云不以慁累閔病而違道云孔子自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='5012:5016'>謂也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='5016:5026'>禮記要義卷第三十</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='5026:5054'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '029-13b' );" name="029-13b" class="pb">[029-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
</p>
